    "causal_summary": "Phase 008 proved why `EMBEDDINGSPROVIDER=auto` silently degrades to the unhealthy `hf-local` fallback even though ollama is up and owns the active vector shard: `factory.ts` reads the active-embedder metadata by shelling out to a bare `sqlite3` binary (`querySqliteScalar` → `execFileSync('sqlite3', …)`), and that helper returns `null` on any error, including `ENOENT`",
